Geonect
_______

3D modeling with Kinect. Uses nestk, which wraps OpenNI and QT.

Installation on OS X
--------------------

mkdir build
cd build
ccmake ..

Set up cmake to use OpenNI and Libfreenect and external OpenCV.

make
./GeonectApp

